        </div>
        <div id="dsq-comment-body-1645" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-1645" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>You missed the whole point of the post you replied to. How can someone as intelligent as you fail to comprehend that the reference to GNOME devs latest brain dead action (the removal of a very useful piece of functionality) was an example of the type of idiocy that seems to pervade the GNOME project</p>
</div>
        </div>

    </li><!-- #comment-## -->
